io.github.u004.steamid.utils

Class USteamCsgo

  • java.lang.Object
    • io.github.u004.steamid.utils.USteamCsgo

  • public final class USteamCsgo
extends Object
    A Steam CS:GO utility.

    USteamCsgo is the utility class to make conversions between SteamId's xuid and CS:GO friend code.

    Since:
    0.1.0
    See Also:
    De- and encoding CS:GO friend codes on UnKnoWnCheaTs, go-csgofriendcode by emily33901 on GitHub

    • Method Detail

      • toFriendCode

        public static io.vavr.control.Try<String> toFriendCode(Long xuid)
        Convert unique Steam account identifier to the interface-friendly CS:GO friend code.

        Calls private static method USteamCsgo#toRawCode(long) and cuts from the start of the code.

        Possible failure exceptions:

        • IllegalArgumentException
        • InvalidCsgoFriendCodeStateException 
        
     // Try.failure(new IllegalArgumentException())
     USteamCsgo.toFriendCode(0);

     // Try.failure(new IllegalArgumentException())
     USteamCsgo.toFriendCode(Long.MAX_VALUE);

     // Try.succes("AJJJS-ABAA")
     USteamCsgo.toFriendCode(1);

     // Try.succes("AEVDG-WQTQ")
     USteamCsgo.toFriendCode(1266042636);
        Parameters:
        xuid - SteamId's xuid
        Returns:
        interface-friendly CS:GO friend code that wrapped in Try

      • fromFriendCode

        public static io.vavr.control.Try<Long> fromFriendCode(String code)
        Convert interface-friendly CS:GO friend code to the unique Steam account identifier.

        Adds to the code and calls private static method USteamCsgo#fromRawCode(String).

        Possible failure exceptions:

        • IllegalArgumentException 
        
     // Try.failure(new IllegalArgumentException())
     USteamCsgo.fromFriendCode(null);

     // Try.failure(new IllegalArgumentException())
     USteamCsgo.fromFriendCode("");

     // Try.success(1)
     USteamCsgo.fromFriendCode("AJJJS-ABAA");

     // Try.success(1)
     USteamCsgo.fromFriendCode("  AJJJS-ABAA  ");

     // Try.success(1266042636)
     USteamCsgo.fromFriendCode("AEVDG-WQTQ");
        Parameters:
        code - interface-friendly CS:GO friend code
        Returns:
        SteamId's xuid that wrapped in Try

      • toFriendCodeRaw

        public static String toFriendCodeRaw(Long xuid)
        Rawly convert unique Steam account identifier to the interface-friendly CS:GO friend code.

        Calls private static method USteamCsgo#toRawCode(long) and cuts from the start of the code. 

        
     // null
     USteamCsgo.toFriendCodeRaw(0);

     // null
     USteamCsgo.toFriendCodeRaw(Long.MAX_VALUE);

     // "AJJJS-ABAA"
     USteamCsgo.toFriendCodeRaw(1);

     // "AEVDG-WQTQ"
     USteamCsgo.toFriendCodeRaw(1266042636);
        Parameters:
        xuid - SteamId's xuid
        Returns:
        interface-friendly CS:GO friend code or null

      • fromFriendCodeRaw

        public static Long fromFriendCodeRaw(String code)
        Rawly convert interface-friendly CS:GO friend code to the unique Steam account identifier.

        Adds to the code and calls private static method USteamCsgo#fromRawCode(String).

     // 1
